Northern Rock May Repurchase Mortgage Loans, Times Reports

-- B y   M i c h e l l e   E .   F r a z e r
-- 
2011-02-13T09:15:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-13/northern-rock-may-repurchase-mortgage-loans-times-reports.html
Northern Rock Plc may buy mortgage
portfolios held by Northern Rock Asset Management Plc, the
Sunday Times reported, citing unidentified people familiar with
the situation.  The purchase could improve Northern Rock’s profitability in
the run-up to the company’s possible sale, the U.K. newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michelle E. Frazer in London at 
 mfrazer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  